snippet.title: Windsor Trailer
snippet.description:
Windsor is a massively multiplayer strategy game. Look forward or backward in time as you plan your moves to bring your kingdom to victory

Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1876070/Windsor__Grand_Strategy_MMO/

Get it on Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gameshovel.windsor&hl=en_US&gl=US

Get it on iOS: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/windsor-grand-strategy/id1612896542
